            <title>[PDFBOX-1349] Postscript tables of truetype fonts are not correctly parsed.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1349</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The specification of the &apos;post&apos; table contains a list of 258 predefined character names.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, the current fontbox interprets name indices &amp;lt;258 in terms of MacRomanEncoding, which is wrong.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Testcase and patch will be attached shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
